OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFuel and excise duty must  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbe replaced with new tax,  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FMPs say                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK needs to create a new motoring  
OL,6, tax to plug the revenue gap as drivers 
OL,7, switch to electric cars, MPs have said.
OL,9,FThe government should tax motorists    
OL,10,Fbased on miles travelled as the use of 
OL,11,Fpetrol and diesel vehicles decreases,  
OL,12,Fthe Transport Select Committee said.   
OL,14,FIf no action is taken this year, the UK
OL,15,Ffaces a #35bn "black hole" in its      
OL,16,Ffinances, they said.                   
OL,18,FThe Treasury said tax revenues would   
OL,19,Fkeep pace with changes prompted by     
OL,20,Felectric vehicle take-up.              
